<i>Deine Schwesterche</i> is in the cupboard.

259
00:18:48,866 --> 00:18:49,839
Cupboard open.

260
00:19:03,753 --> 00:19:04,773
Batskelien!

261
00:19:05,333 --> 00:19:06,393
No!

262
00:19:11,619 --> 00:19:12,460
No!

263
00:19:15,970 --> 00:19:17,019
Batskelien!

264
00:19:18,073 --> 00:19:19,773
What did you do to her?

265
00:19:19,986 --> 00:19:23,893
Come on, you guys!

266
00:19:27,369 --> 00:19:28,489
Why?

267
00:19:29,160 --> 00:19:30,373
Well...

268
00:19:30,612 --> 00:19:32,179
Come on.

269
00:19:32,600 --> 00:19:36,126
Yeah, er... You locked us in
here with the lights off.

270
00:19:37,586 --> 00:19:40,440
I didn't lock you in here
with the lights off at all!

271
00:19:40,983 --> 00:19:42,080
Lights on!

272
00:19:42,966 --> 00:19:44,040
Door open!

273
00:19:48,760 --> 00:19:50,133
But we didn't know that.

274
00:19:50,600 --> 00:19:52,293
And you opened the cupboard.

275
00:19:53,833 --> 00:19:56,133
Yeah, Barteljaap.
You opened the cupboard.

276
00:19:57,086 --> 00:20:01,346
We thought we were in a horror movie.
There's a camera and everything.

277
00:20:01,546 --> 00:20:06,460
I use it to record my classes,
so I can look for what to improve.

278
00:20:07,343 --> 00:20:10,033
Well, if you had paid that
detective a little more...

279
00:20:10,053 --> 00:20:13,033
she would've had phone credit.
- We could've called someone.

280
00:20:13,040 --> 00:20:15,693
I know it seems odd when
you look at it like that...

281
00:20:15,726 --> 00:20:18,946
but she seemed dead and then
she started attacking me!

282
00:20:18,980 --> 00:20:22,533
Oops! That might be my <i>fehler</i>.

283
00:20:23,386 --> 00:20:28,353
I put the Schnaps and the party snacks
with das Mädchen in the cupboard.

284
00:20:29,186 --> 00:20:34,553
But your sister gets a
really bad mean drunk!

285
00:20:35,046 --> 00:20:39,066
It smelled like corpses in here, too.
- Sorry, those were my farts.

286
00:20:39,286 --> 00:20:40,913
I'm insecure about my bowels.

287
00:20:43,526 --> 00:20:46,925
Anyway, luckily you had an
ashtray I could smack her with...

288
00:20:46,926 --> 00:20:48,540
or it might've ended badly.

289
00:20:49,249 --> 00:20:50,200
Ash tray?

290
00:20:54,799 --> 00:20:56,846
No. No!

291
00:20:57,000 --> 00:20:58,206
Mom and dad!

292
00:21:05,800 --> 00:21:07,866
My whole family lies on this floor.

293
00:21:16,903 --> 00:21:19,286
Sorry, what did you say?
- <i>Nichts</i>.

294
00:21:27,326 --> 00:21:28,833
I'm sorry, Barteljaap.

295
00:21:29,507 --> 00:21:31,779
It was just an unfortunate
misunderstanding.

296
00:21:33,009 --> 00:21:34,166
Those happen.

297
00:21:38,690 --> 00:21:39,810
It's okay.

298
00:21:41,066 --> 00:21:45,853
For too long I have let myself get
walked over and get used by everyone!

299
00:21:47,200 --> 00:21:48,906
That all changes now.

300
00:21:49,866 --> 00:21:52,373
I may have lost my
identical twin sister...

301
00:21:52,900 --> 00:21:54,839
but I will refind myself!

302
00:21:55,099 --> 00:21:56,606
It's so sad to look at.

303
00:21:57,567 --> 00:21:59,080
Barteljaap all alone.

304
00:22:03,046 --> 00:22:04,406
No, no, no!

305
00:22:04,486 --> 00:22:06,373
Cancel 'Barteljaap all alone'!

306
00:22:06,493 --> 00:22:07,899
Cancel! Cancel!

307
00:22:17,353 --> 00:22:19,013
If you won't tell anyone...

308
00:22:19,966 --> 00:22:21,160
then I won't either.

309
00:22:26,319 --> 00:22:27,439
Door open!

310
00:22:34,100 --> 00:22:36,719
Sad Barteljaap, all alone.

